"assets include the package archives, Sigstore signature bundles, release "
"notes, and the release SBOM. The same package archives are uploaded to PyPI "
"using trusted publishing, but the Sigstore bundle files are not uploaded to "
"PyPI because the release workflow removes files not accepted by PyPI before "
"publishing."
