"problemas nos textos fonte. O processo real depende se vocأھ usa formatos "
"bilأ­ngues ou monolأ­ngues."

#: workflows.rst:300
msgid ""
"For monolingual formats, source string review functions similarly "
"to :ref:`reviews` â€” once an issue with a source string is reported, the "
"source string is marked as :guilabel:`Needs editing`."
